{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"func","roleHeading":"Function","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"samSelectDetailRegion","externalID":"c:@F@samSelectDetailRegion","modules":[{"name":"DotDocument"}],"fragments":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:I","text":"int"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SamColorImage","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/sam_color_image","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@sam_color_image"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"image"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:I"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:I","text":"int"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"selectedBoundingBox","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":");","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0 on success, or a non-zero error code on failure."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyzes the input image and identifies the most suitable 200x200 pixel"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"region (bounding box) with high level of details that intersects a given bounding box.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is empty (width or height is 0), any region can be selected. Otherwise,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the selected region should have non-empty intersection with this bounding box. The selected region","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"should lie fully inside the input image.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If there is no region satisfying these conditions - if image width or height is smaller than 200","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" lies outside the image, the selected bounding box will be (0, 0, 200, 200).","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["                                  a bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height)."]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["                                  return, contains the bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height),","                                  where width and height are always set to 200."]}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/samSelectDetailRegion"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/dotdocument\/samselectdetailregion"]}],"references":{"doc://DotDocument/documentation/DotDocument/samSelectDetailRegion":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/dotdocument\/samselectdetailregion","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"samSelectDetailRegion","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotDocument\/documentation\/DotDocument\/samSelectDetailRegion","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"}]},"doc://DotDocument/documentation/DotDocument/